## 2. Inputs (Known Variables)

| Variable        | Description                         | Unit        | Example / Value | Source      |
|----------------|-------------------------------------|-------------|----------------:|-------------|
| `FC_AMT`       | Foreign-currency receivable         | EUR         | 4,500,000       | Model       |
| `S₀`           | Current EURUSD spot rate            | USD/EUR     | 1.1517          | Model       |
| `F₀`           | 1-year EURUSD forward rate          | USD/EUR     | 1.0875          | Model       |
| `r_USD`        | USD 1-year interest rate            | %           | 3.68%           | Model       |
| `r_EUR`        | EUR 1-year interest rate            | %           | 2.799%          | Model       |
| `t`            | Time to maturity                    | Years       | 1               | Derived     |
| `K_put`        | EUR Put strike                      | USD/EUR     | N/A (not used)  | Not modeled |
| `K_call`       | EUR Call strike                     | USD/EUR     | Not specified  
